(\frac{m}{n}+\frac{k}{l})a = \frac{mx+ky}{[n,l]}a = mxa' + kya' = \frac{mxa}{[n,l]} + \frac{kya}{[n,l]} = \frac{ma}{n} + \frac{ka}{l}
